				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${J}_{sc}$$\end{document} of 30.09 mA cm−2 and 28.6 mA cm−2, respectively. Further, Nagel et al.9 have improved the light trapping using embedded silicon dioxide (SiO2) nanospheres in TF-SC. Such a structure offers an absorption enhancement of 23.4% relative to the conventional SC.

